This is the Perl module Getopt::Attribute.

INSTALLATION

Getopt::Attribute installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set
up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Getopt::Attribute

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Getopt::Attribute documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Getopt::Attribute

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

